// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0640 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 742348ca-6dcc-5b72-81ab-b2da2cd8dc86

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*almalinux:8*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*")
